#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: docs/howto/en/docbook/howto-interpretation.docbook:260
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Rule 1, definition of \"evil\" and \"eye\" - no help here.  Rule 2, "
